reviews.text: Good service, good taste of soup and food in different styles.

This was a new way of dinning for me. The mode was partial buffet & partial set dinner. The set price included a clay pot style chicken, a traditional style hotpot with a plate of seafood. Vegi and other meats for hotpot as well as regular drinks were buffet style. Chicken was very good and it is worth to try. They also did not cheap out on the seafood plate, both quantity and quality were generous. The place is not the nice kind, but the food is totally worth it. Highly recommended.
Delicious & fresh seafood, close to all kinds of public transport.
Very nice Chicken & hot pot. Recommend the spicy chicken. The seafood hot pot is the signature.

Poor services.
Charge for ONE baby seat even we have 12 adults.
It was stated but not explained in a politr manner

reviews.text: 這間是火鍋自助餐，鍋底可算雞煲，是任吃的，十分美味，環境普通，但食物質素算是很好，宵夜時段更不算貴，性格比高，值得一試。必點海鮮餐，只貴約$40HKD，但物有所值。
Good service, good taste of soup and food in different styles.
鷄煲挺好吃。海鮮拼盤很大堆頭，但不是每款也新鮮味美。火鍋配料中規中矩，限時2.5小時很趕。
招呼週到，食物質素好，每人$3xx, 有獨立房，食足3小時，會再幫襯！
Reserve左8:30，準時去到佢地話執緊枱，等到9:30先入到去..好過分！

reviews.text: Highly recommended. The price is not high not all, but they provide unlimited-refill Chicken hotpot. The seafood is really yummy and fresh. And within the 3 hours time, you can enjoy the chicken hotpot and hotpot with soup. Nice and full.

Food quality is fair but not exceptional tasty. Quite pricy if you are having dinner at MK area *(even hot pot) . The location is good. Staff service really depends on whom is serving your table, ours is not a very nice lady and she always push for quick turnover of the table instead of the consumer need. The toilet is so tiny, even for a small girl to turn around. 

In short, there's always better choice, me personally will not go for second time.

Great choice of chicken pot all you can restaurant.  You can order chicken pot as much as you can, and then come with one portion of fresh beef and seafood for hotpot.  Price is not cheap for all you can eat hotpot, but definitely very reasonable for what they are serving.
Good food in VIP room. Friendly staff.
Yummy spicy chicken pot and seafood hotpot. All you can eat. But environment is just so so

result.name: 新南苑私房菜火鍋鷄煲 San Nam Yuen

reviews.text:
地點又方便， 喺旺角地鐵站一出就到啦。

海鮮火鍋半放題套餐$268
1.麻辣雞煲（不同嘅辣度)
2.選擇湯底打邊爐（八款湯底）
新鮮蟹鍋花甲湯底、澳門豬骨濃湯底、花膠蟲草花椰青湯底、清湯牛腩、四色火鍋、四川麻辣火鍋、海龍王湯底，仲有蕃茄龍蝦湯底(不過呢個要加錢）
3. 海鮮拼盤（六至八款）
4. 任食火鍋配料
5. 本地手切牛頸脊
6. 甜品
7. 涼茶、汽水、果汁任飲

雞煲首先有不同嘅辣到，然後每半分鐘就要先炒一下，服務員亦都好細心幫我地抽出第一次，一打開個嗰蓋真係非常開朗，仲有好濃烈嘅辣椒花椒香味。雞煲嘅雞件都幾嫩滑，食完第一陪，大家都覺得幾好食，忍唔住要再食多盆呢。

跟住我哋就打邊爐，今次我哋叫左個蟹鍋，入邊都差唔多有兩隻蟹，咁個湯底就一定好清甜啦，最吸引我嘅就係一個特大海鮮盤，一行六人嘅海鮮盤真係好巨型，而且每人都有半邊開邊龍蝦🦞，隻龍蝦好大隻，啖啖肉。除咗龍蝦之外，仲有蟶子，大蜆等等。

其實食完海鮮拼盤，已經有啲飽，跟住我哋就點左一啲火鍋料，火鍋配料相對就比較一般，可能因為海鮮好食啦。而火鍋配料丸類不算太多，呢一點就有點失色。
。
埋單後，侍應會送上甜品，每人一客奶凍，都幾滑溜。
總括來講，如果二百幾蚊位，有新鮮海鮮，雖然唔可以咁叫，但係呢個價錢都算合理。

Highly recommended. The price is not high not all, but they provide unlimited-refill Chicken hotpot. The seafood is really yummy and fresh. And within the 3 hours time, you can enjoy the chicken hotpot and hotpot with soup. Nice and full.
食材新鮮，用料足。價錢雖然有d貴，但半任食來說，值回票價。推薦大家去食。
